{"type": "article", "id": 19799, "title": "被“撞击”的灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-28T07:40:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 118, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135014FVvA5dXjk614QcCw.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏灯像是处于科幻电影的某个撞击的瞬间，在原本的正方体上出现了一个缺口，组合在上面的小正方体就有了联动的改变，也让这盏灯有了情节和雕塑感。毫无疑问它是通过电脑建模设计出来的，灯光从打开的缺口里照射出来，一些松动的缝隙也被点亮了，有一种强调的作用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150213B2oc9mTuaFDlbCHP.jpg\" width=\"603\" height=\"363\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60199005\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150214zDFq1motQeYnOGvA.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"361\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.34380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}